To implement a complete Arduino sketch for an object classifier by color using TensorFlow Lite Micro on an Arduino Nano 33 BLE Sense, follow the detailed guidelines outlined below. This involves setting up the environment, loading a model, and performing inference with sensor data. The provided code assumes you have pre-trained a neural network model using TensorFlow and exported it to C++ code suitable for microcontrollers.

